Great British Menu - Season 11, Episodes 11 to 15




North West

This week, two newcomers to the competition are challenging reigning north west champion Matt Worswick. Adam Reid is head chef for one of the UK's leading culinary talents, Simon Rogan, heading up Simon's The French restaurant at Manchester's Midland hotel. And Kim Woodward made history when she was appointed head chef at the Savoy Grill - the first woman to hold this position at the Savoy in its 126-year history.




Original Air Dates: 12-Sep-2016 to 16-Sep-2016
